Package: neuronsDG
Type: Package
Title: Modelling neurons via dichotomized Gaussians
Version: 1.0
Date: 2026-04-01
Author: Michael Barkasi
Maintainer: Michael Barkasi <barkasi@wustl.edu>
Description: Various tools for modeling neurons with dichotomized Gaussians. Defines a Cpp class 'neuron' intended to model a single neuron, accessible through R functions. Provides analysis methods for autocorrelation and cross-correlation.  
License: GPL 3
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.13), RcppEigen, R.matlab, hdf5r, reticulate
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen, BH, MASS
Depends: ggplot2, grid, gridExtra, colorspace
SystemRequirements: NLopt
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
